# ğŸš€ Node.js Clustering + Worker Threads in TypeScript

This project demonstrates how to scale a **Node.js application** using **Clustering** and offload **CPU-intensive tasks** using **Worker Threads**, all written in **TypeScript**.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Features

* âœ… Efficient handling of **high I/O traffic** with **Cluster module**.
* âœ… Offload **CPU-bound computations** (e.g., summing numbers) to **Worker Threads**.
* âœ… Tagged logs for clarity: logs include `process.pid` and thread type.
* âœ… Clean TypeScript structure with logging and error handling.
* âœ… Debug-friendly setup (supports VSCode & Chrome DevTools).

